  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "45 people who wanted to go to Australia were arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sri Lankan Navy has arrested 45 people who tried to go to Australia illegally by sea this morning.",
        "Among those arrested are 11 men and 9 women and 25 people under the age of 20, police said.",
        "The arrested persons have now been taken into custody at the Kuchaveli Police Station and further investigations are being carried out by the Kuchaveli Police.",
        "The Kuchaveli police have also said that they have taken steps to present the arrested suspects in the Trincomalee court today. (a)"
      ],
